.\"returns the evaluation cost remaining
.DT
eval_cost
$MUDNAME$ driver help
eval_cost

.SH Name
.SI 5
eval_cost() - returns the evaluation cost remaining
.EI

.SH Synopsis
.SI 5
int eval_cost( void );
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
eval_cost() returns the number of instructions that can still be executed
before the driver decides it is in an infinite loop.
.EP

.SH See also
.SI 5
set_eval_limit(), reset_eval_cost()
.EI
